 0765            bool isValidObjective = true;
 0766            string objectiveJsonStr = inputAdvisorJsonObject["objective"].ToString();
 767
 0768            JObject objectiveJsonToReturn = JObject.Parse(objectiveJsonStr);
 0769            if (!objectiveJsonToReturn.HasValues)
 0770            {
 0771                return;
 772            }
 0773            JArray endpointArrayToReturn = (JArray)objectiveJsonToReturn["endpoint"];
 0774            JArray objectiveErrorArrayToReturn = (JArray)objectiveJsonToReturn["error"];
 775
 776            //// Following commented code will be using in future
 777            //string schemaPath = Path.GetFullPath(@"..\ProjectManager.Service\InputAdvisorSchema\ObjectiveSchema.json")
 778            //JSchema objectiveSchema = JSchema.Parse(File.ReadAllText(schemaPath));
 0779            JSchema objectiveSchema = JSchema.Parse(schema);
 780
 781            IList<ValidationError> validationErrors;
 0782            bool isValid = objectiveJsonToReturn.IsValid(objectiveSchema, out validationErrors);
 0783            isValidObjective = !isValid ? isValid : isValidObjective;
 784
 0785            objectiveErrorArrayToReturn.Clear();
 786
 0787            var objectiveErrors = from v in validationErrors where !v.Path.Contains("endpoint") select new { v.Path, v.M
 788
 0789            foreach (var error in objectiveErrors)
 0790            {
 0791                objectiveErrorArrayToReturn.Add(ErrorWriter(error.Path, error.Message));
 0792            }
 793
 0794            int endpointCount = 0;
 0795            foreach (var endpoint in endpointArrayToReturn)
 0796            {
 0797                JObject endpointJsonObjectReturn = (JObject)endpoint;
 0798                JArray endpointErrorArray = (JArray)endpointJsonObjectReturn["error"];
 0799                endpointErrorArray.Clear();
 800
 0801                var endpointErrors = from v in validationErrors
 0802                                     where v.Path.Contains("endpoint[" + endpointCount + "]")
 0803                                     select new { v.Path, v.Message };
 804
 0805                foreach (var error in endpointErrors)
 0806                {
 0807                    endpointErrorArray.Add(ErrorWriter(error.Path, error.Message));
 0808                }
 809
 0810                int endpointID = (int)endpointJsonObjectReturn["id"];
 0811                string endpointValue = endpointJsonObjectReturn["Endpoint"].ToString();
 0812                bool isValidEndpoint = ValidateStaticIdAndValue(endpointID, endpointValue, "endpoint");
 0813                if (!isValidEndpoint)
 0814                {
 0815                    isValidObjective = false;
 0816                    endpointErrorArray.Add(ErrorWriter("Endpoint", InputAdvisorConstants.JSON_INVALID_ENDPOINT_OR_ID));
 0817                }
 818
 0819                endpointCount++;
 0820            }
 821
 0822            inputAdvisorJsonObject.Property("validated").Value = isValidObjective;
 0823            inputAdvisorJsonObject.Property("objective").Value = objectiveJsonToReturn;
 0824        }

 02534            'message': {
 02535              '$id': '#/items/properties/error/items/properties/message',
 02536              'type': 'string',
 02537              'title': 'The Message Schema',
 02538              'description': 'An explanation about the purpose of this instance.',
 02539              'default': '',
 02540              'examples': [
 02541                'Error Message'
 02542              ]
 02543            }
 02544          }
 02545        }
 02546      }
 02547    }
 02548  }
 02549}";
 2550
 02551            bool isValidMarketAccess = true;
 02552            string marketAccessJsonStr = inputAdvisorJsonObject["marketAccess"].ToString();
 2553
 02554            JArray marketAccessJsonArrayToReturn = JArray.Parse(marketAccessJsonStr);
 02555            if (!marketAccessJsonArrayToReturn.HasValues)
 02556            {
 02557                return;
 2558            }
 2559
 2560            //// Following commented code will be using in future. GetFullPath won't work while deploy.
 2561            //string schemaPath = Path.GetFullPath(@"..\ProjectManager.Service\InputAdvisorSchema\MarketAccessSchema.jso
 2562            //JSchema marketAccessSchema = JSchema.Parse(File.ReadAllText(schemaPath));
 02563            JSchema marketAccessSchema = JSchema.Parse(schema);
 2564
 2565            IList<ValidationError> validationErrors;
 02566            bool isValid = marketAccessJsonArrayToReturn.IsValid(marketAccessSchema, out validationErrors);
 2567
 02568            isValidMarketAccess = !isValid ? isValid : isValidMarketAccess;
 2569
 02570            int marketAccessCount = 0;
 02571            foreach (var marketAccess in marketAccessJsonArrayToReturn)
 02572            {
 02573                JObject marketAccessJsonObjectReturn = (JObject)marketAccess;
 02574                JArray marketAccessErrorArray = (JArray)marketAccessJsonObjectReturn["error"];
 02575                marketAccessErrorArray.Clear();
 2576
 02577                var marketAccessErrors = from v in validationErrors
 02578                                         where v.Path.StartsWith("[" + marketAccessCount + "]")
 02579                                         select new { v.Path, v.Message };
 2580
 02581                foreach (var error in marketAccessErrors)
 02582                {
 02583                    marketAccessErrorArray.Add(ErrorWriter(error.Path, error.Message));
 02584                }
 2585
 02586                marketAccessCount++;
 02587            }
 2588
 02589            inputAdvisorJsonObject.Property("validated").Value = isValidMarketAccess;
 02590            inputAdvisorJsonObject.Property("marketAccess").Value = marketAccessJsonArrayToReturn;
 02591        }
